{"title":"我热爱北京","authors":["阿列克斯·恰奇"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":11,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我热爱北京"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔阿尔巴尼亚诗人〕阿列克斯·恰奇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我热爱北京。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转瞬之间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它有多么大的变化！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨天我看到了什么，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天我又看到了什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"低矮的房屋哪里去了？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贫困的生活哪里去了？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平地升起了一座座的宫殿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连人们的目光也都已经改变。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颐和园偷偷躲在角落里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好像还在怀疑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这些变化……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"皇帝怎么能想到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民大踏步地冲破了一切。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我漫步在宽阔的街道上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿着整洁的人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"了解他们要到哪里去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因此步伐坚定。……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢水像大江似地滚流。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里是多么清洁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到处开遍了菊花！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京发言了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全中国正在建设。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京发言了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全亚洲都在倾听。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地拉那也是那样高兴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我热爱北京"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里多么温暖！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新中国的心脏在跳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我从这里看到了未来。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔李宁来译〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}